biolockj

Class BioModuleFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • biolockj.BioModuleFactory

  • public class BioModuleFactory
extends Object
    This class initializes pipeline modules, startign with those in the Config file and adding the prerequisite and post-requisite modules.

      • ALLOW_IMPLICIT_MODULES

        protected static final String ALLOW_IMPLICIT_MODULES
        Config Boolean property: "project.allowImplicitModules"
        If set to "Y", implicit modules can be directly configured. Otherwise, these modules can only by automatically added to pipelines by BioLockJ.

      • buildModules

        public static List<BioModule> buildModules()
                                    throws Exception
        The method returns the ordered list of BioModules required as part of the runtime Config file.
        Each line the begins with "#BioModule" should be followed by the full class name of a Java class that implements the BioModule interface.
        Returns:
        List of BioModules
        Throws:
        Exception - thrown for invalid BioModules
